OL,4,CMillions struggle to pay broadband
OL,5,Cbills in UK
OL,6, About 2.5 million people in the UK are
OL,7, behind on broadband payments, according
OL,8, to a survey from Citizens Advice.
OL,10,FThe number has jumped by about 700,000
OL,11,Fsince before the pandemic, when 1.8
OL,12,Fmillion people owed money to their
OL,13,Fprovider.
OL,15,FYoung people and those with children
OL,16,Funder 18 were worst affected.
OL,18,FHouseholds receiving universal credit
OL,19,Fwere nine times more likely to be
OL,20,Fbehind on their broadband bills than
OL,21,Fthose who were not.
